title: Live: Central Fla. HS football scores
text:
Central Florida high school football scoreboard News 6 airs 6 Yard Line on Fridays at 11 p.m. Published On: Sep 17 2015 02:42:18 PM EDT Updated On: Oct 24 2015 12:28:34 AM EDT 
Check back for live scoring updates to high school football games in Central Florida.
